"title": "3045: Holy Spirit, sovereignty of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3045",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit has supreme power and acts in accordance with divine purposes, exercising authority and control in the world and over God's people.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit is Lord</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:17-2Cor3:18\">2CO 3:17–3:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">JDG 3:10</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit is sovereign in bringing spiritual life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:1-John3:8\">JHN 3:1–3:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:63\">JHN 6:63</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:2\">ROM 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:5\">TIT 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:2\">1PE 1:2</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's will is sovereign</h2>\n<h3>He determines the distribution of spiritual gifts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1SA 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:20\">1SA 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:23\">1SA 19:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:4\">HEB 2:4</a></p>\n<h3>He controls the appointment of leaders</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:2\">ACT 13:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:28\">ACT 20:28</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit demonstrates his sovereignty over creation</h2>\n<h3>He participates in the work of creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:30\">PSA 104:30</a></p>\n<h3>He performs miraculous deeds</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:39\">ACT 8:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:12\">1KI 18:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:16\">2KI 2:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:28-Matt12:38\">MAT 12:28–12:38</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:22-Mark3:30\">MRK 3:22–3:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:14-Luke11:23\">LUK 11:14–11:23</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit exercises his rule in the lives of individuals</h2>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is led by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:1\">MAT 4:1</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:12\">MRK 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:1\">LUK 4:1</a></p>\n<h3>God's people are led by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:18\">GAL 5:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10\">PSA 143:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:20\">MAT 10:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:27\">LUK 2:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:29\">ACT 8:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:22\">ACT 20:22</a></p>\n<h3>God's people are restrained by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:6-Acts16:7\">ACT 16:6–16:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>God's people are given victory by the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">JDG 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:6\">JDG 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">JDG 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">JDG 15:14</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit's sovereignty is confirmed by the greatness of his attributes</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:7\">PSA 139:7</a> <em>His presence</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4\">1CO 2:4</a> <em>His power</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:10-1Cor2:11\">1CO 2:10–2:11</a> <em>His knowledge</em></p>",
